author: Epic Games
description:
When darkness fell, The Krasue awakened… 
Inspired by Thai folklore, play as The Krasue, a gruesome Killer with two terrifying forms, and Vee Boonyasak, an electrifying survivor from the rising punk band Axekick. Step into a terrifying world rooted in visceral body-horror. 
Dead by Daylight: Sinister Grace, Now Available on the Epic Games Store! https://epic.gm/dbd-sg
title: Dead by Daylight | Sinister Grace
